snippet.title: The Company Of Myself - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
The Company Of Myself is a really amazing flash game, where you have to duplicate yourself in order to complete a level. When you duplicate yourself, you must choose the course you want your duplication to follow, and try to make a co-operating path to help yourself reach the exit. Enjoy this video walkthrough, even if I've made some mistakes :D
